of being here20 years from now.

38:24.844 --> 38:27.346
I can't... I can't thinklike that, Caroline.

38:27.388 --> 38:28.681
I just...

38:28.723 --> 38:31.309
(sighs)

38:39.066 --> 38:42.903
CAROLINE:I knew that if he had the courage to risk dying,

38:42.945 --> 38:46.073
I had to have the courage to risk living.

38:46.115 --> 38:49.702
So I just concentrated on feeling close to him.

38:49.744 --> 38:52.621
(lively 1940s pop music playing)

38:52.663 --> 38:55.291
(airplane engine humming)

39:00.421 --> 39:02.340
(sniffles)

39:15.061 --> 39:17.813
I wrote him every day.

39:19.774 --> 39:21.692
Sometimes twice.

39:21.734 --> 39:22.818
Take it easy.

39:22.860 --> 39:24.779
Okay. Oh.

39:30.409 --> 39:33.371
♪ ♪

39:34.330 --> 39:36.373
(music continues over radio)

39:58.938 --> 40:00.564
Mr. Myers!

40:00.606 --> 40:01.982
Hi.

