Thomas got stronger by the dayand joined us.

01:15:03.040 --> 01:15:06.877
Sometimes, enemy Japanesepatrols would come by.

01:15:06.919 --> 01:15:09.922
If we saw them,we would kill them.

01:15:09.963 --> 01:15:11.798
Sometimes,they would forget to come,

01:15:11.840 --> 01:15:15.385
so we would go looking.

01:15:32.110 --> 01:15:33.695
It's all right, Morang.

01:15:33.737 --> 01:15:35.864
It's all right.

