listed as missing in actionfor 66 years, has been found.

01:23:06.564 --> 01:23:08.066
(gasps)

01:23:08.108 --> 01:23:11.194
I am deeply honoredto deliver to you

01:23:11.236 --> 01:23:13.363
the personal effectsof your husband,

01:23:13.405 --> 01:23:15.532
which were recovered.

01:23:32.882 --> 01:23:35.969
I've been further authorizedto inform you

01:23:36.011 --> 01:23:37.178
that the following awards

01:23:37.220 --> 01:23:39.305
have been recommended bythe Secretary of the Navy

01:23:39.347 --> 01:23:41.182
on behalf of agrateful nation.

01:23:41.224 --> 01:23:44.602
For meritorious conductin the face of the enemy

01:23:44.644 --> 01:23:46.062
and for gallantry

01:23:46.062 --> 01:23:49.065
above and beyond the call ofduty, Lieutenant Neil Thomas,

01:23:49.065 --> 01:23:52.152
