a Purple Heart, the Silver Starand the Navy Cross.

01:23:56.406 --> 01:23:57.824
(gasps softly)

01:24:05.957 --> 01:24:07.333
Thank you.

01:24:10.211 --> 01:24:11.755
Thank you both

01:24:11.755 --> 01:24:13.506
very much.

